%N A397094 Numerators of coefficients in expansion of Product_{k>=1} (1+x^k)^(k/2).
%C A397094 G.f. of a(n)/A046161(n) is the square root of the g.f. for A026007.
%F A397094 a(n) / A046161(n) ~ zeta(3)^(1/6) * exp(3^(4/3) * zeta(3)^(1/3) * n^(2/3) / 2^(5/3)) / (2^(7/8) * 3^(1/3) * sqrt(Pi) * n^(2/3)).
